        How Council Zoning Affects What Buyers Can Do With Your Brisbane Property
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Zoning determines your property's development potential, renovation scope, and ceiling price. Here's what Brisbane sellers need to understand before they list.
      </p>
